167353.en:
<start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>It's good on the way there, but scary
on the way back.<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>

167354.en:
<start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>The hand that has removed the evil
spirits is beautifully done.<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>

167355.en:
<start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>But watch your back. The walkers are
always sneaking up behind you.<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>

167356.en:
<start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>We are Yoi, the head of the Yinshu,
the Yin branch of the druid.<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>

167357.en:
<start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>You must be the new guy in Yang
Clan.Poor guy, being played by a no-
nonsense woman.<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>

167358.en:
<start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>We Yinshu are masters of witchcraft.
If you want to be strong as a druid,
come to us anytime.<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>

167359.en: <start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>I know it's true, but ...<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>

167360.en:
<start_lip_sync n05099 _normal m00001>If you are going to call yourself Yang
Clan from now on, watch your back at
best.<stop_lip_animation n05099 CLOSE_MOUTH>
